title: Shutdown Fullcast 7.20 - Fight, Fly, and Grift Into Week 1
description:
After Stanford bravely faced the trials of Week 0.36, we're finally ready to lap up FIVE STRAIGHT DAYS of college football. Florida State-Alabama! West Virginia-Virginia Tech! Michigan-The Shell of a Florida Team That We Didn't Believe In At The Time We Recorded This And Then Somehow More Players Got Suspended! What else are we, the most and only podcast about the sport focused on?Orgeron-Sitake WrasslinWhy neutral site games are fine, if one of the teams is PurdueJIMBO TO UAB RUMORZUnranked teams that probably won't beat ranked opponents but it's funny to consider if they doOur upgraded spokesman for Dr. Pepper, mustachioed detective Barry CulpepperHow to lose in Kirk Ferentz's Low Calorie Casino
